    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The validation campaign conducted in 2022 demonstrates CFD model accuracy for RH index prediction within ±12% across the adult operating envelope. The Q3 2023 expansion of the indicated population to include pediatric patients (BSA 0.5–1.0 m², flows 1.0–2.0 L/min) was reviewed by the assessment team, which concluded that dimensional similarity and consistent model physics provide adequate confidence that prior validation evidence extends to the pediatric subgroup without requiring additional experimental validation runs. Overall credibility is assessed as sufficient to support the Accepted decision at Medium assurance level.",
